## ✅ **WHAT THIS FILE CONTAINS:**

### **Dependencies:**
- **express** (v4.18.2) - Web server framework
- **compression** (v1.7.4) - Gzip compression middleware

### **Dev Dependencies:**
- **nodemon** (v3.0.1) - Auto-restart server on file changes (for local development)

### **Scripts:**
- `npm start` - Starts production server
- `npm run dev` - Starts development server with auto-reload

### **Engine Requirements:**
- Node.js 18+ required
- npm 9+ required

